10. the fan of metal is between the fan of indie and the person who's hobby is board-games##2
11. the fan of disco is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
12. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
13. the fan of pop is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the fan of reggae##2
14. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
15. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the car##1
